PrecisEnactment of the NOTICE OF BRANCH CLOSURE (COOPERATIVE CREDIT ASSOCIATIONS) REGULATIONS whereby cooperative credit societies will be required to give four months' notice to its customers, the public and the Commissioner, prior to the closing of a branch located in an urban area, and six months' notice in rural areas.
